Specify a JNDI name of the {@link java.util.concurrent.Executor} to delegate to,_replacing the default JNDI name "java:comp/DefaultManagedScheduledExecutorService"._

This can either be a fully qualified JNDI name, or the JNDI name relative_to the current environment naming context if "resourceRef" is set to "true"._@see #setConcurrentExecutor_@see #setResourceRef
